dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially. Inset: Harlech. Shows hundreds and main roads. Descriptive text on verso with caption title: Merioneth-Shire. Book 2, Chap. XI. Fol. 117-118; signature GgI. From: The theatre of the Empire of Great Britaine ... / divided and described by John Speed. London : And are to be solde by I. Sudbury and G. Humble, 1611.
